public static enum IAccessGroup.ReadAccessContextType
extends java.lang.Enum<IAccessGroup.ReadAccessContextType>

Represents the types of read access contexts that can be maintained by the members that make up the group

Enum Constant Summary
CONTRIBUTOR
          A context representing a single contributor
MEMBERS
          A context of only the direct members and administrators of the process area
SUB_HIERARCHY
          A context including the members/administrators of this process area, as well as those of all team areas below it in the hierarchy
